Package: scDIFtest
Type: Package
Title: Item-Wise Score-Based DIF tests
Version: 0.1.0-01
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dries", "Debeer", email = "debeer.dries@gmail.com", 
    role = c("cre", "aut")))
Description: This R-package can be used for item-wise DIF tests for fitted
            \code{\link{mirt}}, \code{\link{multipleGroup}} or 
            \code{\link{bfactor}} models. Under the hood the 
            \code{\link{sctest}} from the \code{\link{strucchange}}-package is
            used.
Imports: sandwich, 
         strucchange, 
         mirt,
         zoo,
Suggests: mvtnorm
